channel.title: A webclient problem?
channel.description:
EDIT:
I .ziped the whole cache instead of all the files inside the cache, would this be what is causing it?
[hr]
Hey guys, apparently my webclient's cache isn't downloading properly (or something) .. It might've been something to do with how I jar'ed it. This is my [url=http://www.velious.webs.com]site[/url]
It seems no one can download it properly, yet I can play on it. Although i think it's because I had the cache downloaded before i put it up there.

I think so. If thats the case then when you downloading the cache it will unzip the folder into another folder in your C:. So ZIP the cache itself. not the folder that is holding the cache
